name: Skywalker Pilot
description: Wanted: Yeti foe, L. Skywalker, for the dismemberment of fellow yeti, Mr. Telford Wampa, who was attacked in his rental cave while on summer holiday on Hoth. L. Skywalker is considered to be highly dangerous and is wanted for the mass murder of workers and destruction of a local space station. Limited to 10 editions.
